%N A394925 Numbers k such that sigma(k) = psi(k) + tau(k) + Omega(k)^6.
%e A394925 10936 is a term since sigma(10936) = 20520 = 16416 + 8 + 4^6 = psi(10936) + tau(10936) + Omega(10936)^6.
%o A394925 (PARI) isok(k) = {my(f = factor(k)); sigma(f) == prod(i=1, #f~, (f[i, 1]+1) * f[i, 1]^(f[i, 2]-1)) + numdiv(f) + bigomega(f)^6; } \\ _Amiram Eldar_, Apr 07 2026
